                <h2 class="font-medium text-2xl">Cardiotel LN</h2>
                <p class="text-base">
                    Telmisartan IP 40 mg +  Cilnidipine 10 mg Tablets. In HTN with Diabetes or CKD uncontrolled with monotherapy
                </p>
                <ul class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-4">
                
                    <li><span class="font-normal">In HTN with Diabetes or CKD uncontrolled with monotherapy</li>
                    <li><span class="font-semibold">Quality Certification</span> - WHO, GMP</li>
                </ul>
            
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col bg-white rounded-md">
            <img
                src="/cb25.png"
                alt=""
                class="h-[50vh] object-cover"
            />
            <div class="p-5 flex flex-col gap-2">
                <h2 class="font-medium text-2xl">Cardiotel BETA 25</h2>
                <p class="text-base">
                    Telmisartan IP 40mg +
MetoProlol Succinate 25 mg (ER) Tablet
                </p>
