                <p class="text-base">
                    Telmisartan IP 40mg +
                    MetoProlol Succinate 50 mg (ER) Tablet
                </p>
                <ul class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-4">
                
                    <li><span class="font-normal">In The Management of Hypertension with CAD.</li>
