                <h2 class="font-medium text-2xl">Victobet LN 50/10</h2>
                <p class="text-base">
                    Metoorolol Succinate (ER) &
Cinidipine Tablets
                </p>
                <ul class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-4">
                
                    <li><span class="font-normal">For superior control of hypertension and nephro-safety.</li>
                    <li><span class="font-semibold">Quality Certification</span> - WHO, GMP</li>
                </ul>
            
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
